item.title: Prayer bpn13080 in Hiri Motu
item.description: Oiemu keruma henunai lau noga, lauegu Dirava e! bona ia namo bema Oiemu henari ia tahua tauna ia noho Oiemu naria Helaga Gabuna bona Oiemu gimaia ena Goada Rumana dekenai. Lauegu Lohia e, lauegu lalona oi hadiaria, Oiemu Hahedinaraia Herevadia ena hairai dekenai, Oiemu hariharibada amo, daba diari dekenai, lauegu taunanina Oi hadiaria hegeregerena. (Source category: DABAI GURIGURI) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13080)
